Rogue boots are pieces of armour, which provide +2 bonuses to all Defence types. The boots cannot be crafted, are untradeable, and can be stored in the costume room of a player-owned house.

There is a 1/8 chance of obtaining a piece of rogue equipment when a player successfully cracks the safe at the end of the Rogues' Den maze.
